Challenge Template:

1. Describe the Problem

As a user
So that I can keep track of my tasks
I want to check if a text includes the string #TODO.

2. Design the Function Signature

def task_checker("text"):

    Returns a boolean if "#TODO" present.

    Side Effects:
    - Throws error if input not string.


3. Create Examples as Tests

- Throws error if input not string.
check_if_string(12) => Error

- #TODO present with task
if_contains_to_do("#TODO washing up) => True

- No #TODO 
if_doesnt_contain_to_do("washing up) => False

-TODO with no #
to_do_no_hash("TODO washing up") => False

-Check if  #TODO and task
todo_and_task("#TODO") => False